modelVersions.description:
more updates overtime but for my 2nd LoRA it's Saori from Blue Archive, Enjoy

  • Update the webui by using the git pull command or by downloading it again

  • Copy the LoRA file to the stable-diffusion-webui/models/lora directory

  • Choose your desired LoRA as demonstrated in a video tutorial

  • Adjust the weight as necessary (default weight of 1 is often too high)
